/* unit_datatype.pk - Synthetic checks for the bounded, depth-guarded datatype
   validator (h5_walk.pk h5policy_dtype_check).  These craft datatype blobs in
   memory, so they exercise the recursion cap and bounds handling precisely,
   without needing a full HDF5 file.  Run via h5policy/tests/run.sh.

   Prints one "PASS <name>" / "FAIL <name> ..." line per case and exits 0 only
   if every case passed.  */

/* Copyright (C) 2026 The HDF Group.  */

